data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Beautiful 2-bed, 2.5-bath townhome located in Lynwood at Meadow Woods features a pleasant water view and an A+ floor plan! Wood laminate floors throughout. Fresh paint. Dual masters upstairs and living area with full kitchen suite, dining nook, living room and 1/2 bath downstairs. 1 car garage. Lovely rear lanai with pond view. Lynwood community is conveniently located to OIA, 417, Florida's Turnpike, retail, shopping and dining! Investor Friendly. HOA Fee includes Water and Sewer. Don’t miss this opportunity and see all this awesome home has to offer before it’s gone!
